== Overview ==
The Vidian Industries Heavy Shield Disruptor was designed to counter the use of heavier shielding technologies and deflective capabilities.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Heavy Shield Disruptor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
